íŸ@c59a5de82ce2d4c0e71b4e5bacae494933dc0cbce1d231a778ce25c137a98bb7⁄2Title: title: split words
Path: Flags
Content:
``--min-word-length, -l {int}``
: The minimum word length.
``--grapheme-clusters, -g``
: Measure word length in grapheme clusters (requires -l).
``--utf-8-bytes, -b``
: Measure word length in UTF-8 bytes (default; requires -l; non-ASCII chars are length 2+).
